  "keyFeatures": [
    "Built-in Mihomo (Clash Meta) core with Alpha channel support",
    "Cross-platform: Windows (x64/x86/ARM), macOS (Intel/Apple Silicon), Linux (x64/arm64)",
    "Profile management with remote/local/merge/script types",
    "Profile enhancement via Merge configs and JavaScript scripting",
    "System proxy and TUN (virtual NIC) mode",
    "Visual proxy group and rule editor",
    "Real-time connections, logs, and traffic monitoring",
    "WebDAV-based configuration backup and sync",
